## API 엔드포인트

### 인증 (Auth)

#### 일반 회원가입

```http
POST /auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "user@example.com",
  "password": "password123",
  "username": "홍길동"
}
```

#### 초대 링크로 회원가입

```http
POST /auth/register/invite
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "user@example.com",
  "password": "password123",
  "username": "홍길동",
  "inviteCode": "abc12345"
}
```

#### 로그인

```http
POST /auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "user@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}
```

#### 내 정보 조회

```http
GET /auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {accessToken}
```

### 팀 (Teams)

#### 팀 생성

```http
POST /teams
Authorization: Bearer {accessToken}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "개발팀",
  "description": "프론트엔드 개발팀",
  "isPublic": false
}
```

#### 내가 속한 팀 목록

```http
GET /teams
Authorization: Bearer {accessToken}
```

#### 팀 상세 정보

```http
GET /teams/{teamId}
Authorization: Bearer {accessToken}
```

#### 팀 멤버 목록

```http
GET /teams/{teamId}/members
Authorization: Bearer {accessToken}
```

#### 초대 코드 재생성

```http
POST /teams/{teamId}/invite/regenerate
Authorization: Bearer {accessToken}
```

#### 초대 코드로 팀 정보 조회

```http
GET /teams/join/{inviteCode}
Authorization: Bearer {accessToken}
```

#### 초대 코드로 팀 참여

```http
POST /teams/join/{inviteCode}
Authorization: Bearer {accessToken}
```

#### 멤버 제거

```http
DELETE /teams/{teamId}/members/{userId}
Authorization: Bearer {accessToken}
```

#### 멤버 권한 변경

```http
PATCH /teams/{teamId}/members/{userId}/role
Authorization: Bearer {accessToken}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "role": "admin"
}
```